title: FC Spitak
text:
Spitak Football Club (), is a defunct <a href="Armenia">Armenia</a>n <a href="association%20football">football</a> club from the town of <a href="Spitak">Spitak</a>, <a href="Lori%20Province">Lori Province</a>.
The club was dissolved in 1999 and is currently inactive from professional football.
